SUB_W02_EVAR_SIUG_AMYA_YELLOW_CASTLE_020.text:
Sure, but there's no WAY she's a golem.
Now let's go talk to the Yellow Sage;
I bet she'll know something.

SUB_W02_EVAR_SIUG_AMYA_YELLOW_CASTLE_040.text:
She does not wish the girl to fail;
she will pretend not to notice even
if she does catch wind of our scheme.

SUB_W02_EVAR_SIUG_AMYA_COLOR_QUEST_RED_0.text:
This is the Squire's Burg, where they all live.
All witches have to respect them here;
the others get cranky if you don't.
